OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Racism affected our       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftreatment in Horizon       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fscandal'                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Seven Post Office workers of South     
OL,6, Asian heritage have told the BBC they  
OL,7, believe racism affected the way people 
OL,8, were treated in the Horizon scandal.   
OL,10,FOne of the workers who spoke to BBC    
OL,11,FNewsnight said: "It felt like they     
OL,12,Fthought that you were a foreigner and  
OL,13,Fyou'd robbed them."                    
OL,15,FThe Horizon scandal saw 700            
OL,16,Fsub-postmasters prosecuted from 1999 to
OL,17,F2015, with some going to prison.       
OL,19,FPost Office says it aims to "get to the
OL,20,Ftruth of what went wrong in the past". 
